WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Murakaza neza kuri Simba Supermarket Live Selling!

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Uyu munsi dufite ibicuruzwa byiza ku mbuto n'imboga nshya.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Reba pome nziza, 500 RWF gusa kuri kg!

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Dufite kandi inyanya nshya ku 300 RWF kuri kg.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Ntutakaze ibyiza byacu kuri banana!

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Tanga ubu ubone gutwarwa kubuntu ku bicuruzwa birenze 10,000 RWF.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Murakoze kureba! Ongeraho ibicuruzwa muri cart yawe ubu.
